PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FJust hours before speaking to the
OL,8,FPress Association, Holly was leading a
OL,9,Fwalking group as part of her career as
OL,10,Fa support worker for Change Grow Live,
OL,11,Fwhere she uses her experience to help
OL,12,Fothers.
OL,14,FYet previously, after having a
OL,15,Ftraumatic time at university, Holly
OL,16,Fdid not drink any other liquid apart
OL,17,Ffrom alcohol for three years and was
OL,18,Fno stranger to starting her day with a
OL,19,Fpint of cider.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
