PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHolly, who lives near Southport,
OL,8,FMerseyside, told PA: "I truly,
OL,9,Fwholeheartedly was going to die. I was
OL,10,Ftold I was going to die. I believed it
OL,11,Fand I had no hope.
OL,13,F"But here I am, nearly three years
OL,14,Flater, working in addiction and
OL,15,Frunning a half marathon. These are all
OL,16,Fthings that I could only dream of and
OL,17,Fnow I'm actually doing it."
OL,26,@pD@VOUuD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
