PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHolly's dependency on alcohol
OL,8,Fescalated rapidly in her mid-20s and
OL,9,Fshe turned from drinking prosecco with
OL,10,Fher family in the evenings to
OL,11,Fexperiencing physical withdrawals if
OL,12,Fshe went without a drink.
OL,14,F"If I was going out, I'd have to take
OL,15,Fa bottle of wine and I would put it
OL,16,Finto three smaller bottles so I could
OL,17,Fhide them in a bag and I was just
OL,18,Fliving in fear every single day," she
OL,19,Fsad.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"I went to hospital numerous times, I
OL,8,Fhad severe liver disease and then, in
OL,9,F2023, I went in again and I was really
OL,10,Funwell this time. I'd been vomiting
OL,11,Fblood and all sorts, and they said to
OL,12,Fme there, you are going to die in six
OL,13,Fmonths if you carry on like this.
OL,15,F"But even that didn't stop me. It
OL,16,Fupset me but I didn't care. I'd kind
OL,17,Fof accepted the fact I was going to
OL,18,Fdie because I can't stop this."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
