FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHolly said negative stereotypes
OL,8,Fsurrounding alcohol addiction prompted
OL,9,Fher to speak out.
OL,11,F"I'm not your stereotypical
OL,12,Falcoholic," she said.
OL,14,F"I was a young girl when I got trapped
OL,15,Fin that cycle and I think stereotypes
OL,16,Fcan be a barrier to people seeking and
OL,17,Fgetting help.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@KO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"Equally, I don't think alcohol
OL,8,Faddiction is spoken about enough. I
OL,9,Fthink there's so much stigma and
OL,10,Fstereotypes attached to it and the
OL,11,Fstigma's awful."
OL,13,FHolly lost her fitness while dependent
OL,14,Fon alcohol as she would spend large
OL,15,Famounts of time lying in bed and
OL,16,Fdrinking and Sunday's half marathon is
OL,17,Fa testament to her recovery.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775916666
OL,3,CWoman who drank two litres of gin a
OL,4,Cday set to run half marathon for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"When I was drinking, I did nothing.
OL,8,FAll I'd do is lie in bed and drink.
OL,9,FSo, when I got sober, getting my
OL,10,Ffitness back was really important and
OL,11,FI've always, always loved running,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,FHolly said the half marathon was more
OL,15,Fthan a physical challenge and is a way
OL,16,Fto give back, raise awareness, and
OL,17,Fshow that recovery is possible.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
